<blockquote>
  <p>The authentication system in Django aims to be very generic and doesnâ€™t provide some features commonly found in web authentication systems. Solutions for some of these common problems have been implemented in third-party packages:</p>
</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li>Password strength checking</li>
  <li>Throttling of login attempts</li>
  <li>Authentication against third-parties (OAuth, for example)</li>
  <li>Object-level permissions</li>
</ul>

